Nyamwasa trial: Four guilty of shooting Rwandan - in 15 seconds

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Four men have been found guilty of trying to murder Rwanda's former army chief, Gen Faustin Kayumba Nyamwasa.

